title: Sunset Dreams
description: I painted this sunset because it reminds me of peace and happiness. I used watercolors to blend the colors together.

title: My Robot Friend
description: This is my dream robot that helps kids with homework and makes learning fun!

title: The Magic Forest
description: A short story about a girl who discovers a magical forest where animals can talk and trees sing songs.

title: How Plants Grow
description: My science experiment showing how different amounts of water affect plant growth over 2 weeks.

title: Stop Motion Adventure
description: A 2-minute stop motion animation about a toy's journey around my house. Took me 3 days to make!

title: Underwater World
description: I drew all my favorite sea creatures using colored pencils. The octopus was the hardest part!

title: The Lost Puppy
description: A heartwarming tale about a puppy who gets lost but finds his way home with help from kind strangers.

title: Volcano Eruption Model
description: I built a working volcano model and explained the chemical reaction that makes it erupt!

title: My Day in Drawings
description: A comic strip showing everything I do from morning to night. Drawing breakfast was fun!

title: Cooking Tutorial
description: Teaching other kids how to make their own pizza! It's easier than you think and so yummy.

title: Space Explorer
description: My poem about traveling to different planets and meeting friendly aliens who love Earth music.

title: Rainbow Bridge
description: An acrylic painting of a rainbow bridge over a river. I love how the colors reflect in the water!
